Clockcal is a simple program displaying an analog clock with sweeping
second hand and a scrolling calendar. Press 'i' to show a static display
of day, date, month, year and time. Press 'c' to show the current month's
calendar. Press the left or right cursor buttons to scroll the calendar
view backwards or forwards one month at a time. Press 'h' for help. Press
'q' to quit, or press "MyPrograms" to exit.
